---
description: HeatHub product and engineering guardrails
alwaysApply: true
---

HeatHub is an information aggregation and search platform.

Never implement ecommerce features:

- cart
- checkout
- payment
- orders
- refunds
- inventory
- logistics

Implement search, comparison, map discovery, weather context, merchant redirects, and affiliate click tracking.

Use TypeScript strict mode, reusable components, mobile-first UI, and SEO-friendly pages.
